    "body": "When installing Boost@1.54.0 with python3, spack cannot patch boost.build and throws an error:\r\n```\r\nStaging archive: *****/boost_1_54_0.tar.bz2\r\nThe text leading up to this was:\r\n--------------------------\r\n|diff --git a/tools/build/src/tools/python.jam b/tools/build/src/tools/python.jam\r\n|index 90377ea..123f66a 100644\r\n|--- a/tools/build/src/tools/python.jam\r\n|+++ b/tools/build/src/tools/python.jam\r\n--------------------------\r\n```\r\nThis is due to a change in the directory structure of boost.build. For versions before 1.56.0 the path should be `/tools/build/v2/tools/python.jam`",
